jobDescription:
About the job

We are looking for a Back-end Developer / Engineer to join our team. You will be responsible in the development and maintenance of back-end systems . Your expertise in web technologies will help us deliver quality products that captivate our audience.




Job Responsibilities:

Lead the technical architecture and feature design of business systems and oversee code implementation；
Participate in the development and maintenance of internal information systems；
Contribute to the development and maintenance of internal workflow platforms.




Job Requirements:

Bachelor's degree in Computer Science, Software Engineering, or any related field
Proficiency in the Java programming language, with expertise in mainstream technologies such as I/O, multithreading, Spring Boot, Spring Cloud, and MyBatis;
Proficiency in common databases and middleware, including MySQL, Redis, RocketMQ, and Elasticsearch;
Familiarity with design patterns and practical experience in abstract modeling, with a preference for candidates with domain model design experience in previous projects;
Sensitivity to business needs, with a track record of leading or participating in large-scale business software platform projects and serving as a core developer, with a preference for experience in process systems and middleware development;
Self-driven, skilled at identifying and articulating insights, and proactive in driving solutions;
Strong ability to proactively facilitate issue resolution among team members.
